They are blocking myspace at work. So until I can find the time to set up remote desktop here, I will be using livejournal again... only I picked up a few people at myspace who want to be able to read it, and I cannot figure out how to make this public again since they've made all the changes, and I don't have time to keep trying... SO - I moved. THIS is me.

Feel free to add, or not, as pleases you. :)
